
This is the Perl distribution Getopt-Attribute.

## Installation

Getopt-Attribute installation is straightforward.
If your CPAN shell is set up, you should just be able to do

    % cpan Getopt::Attribute

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

## Documentation

Getopt-Attribute documentation is available as in POD.
So you can do:

    % perldoc Getopt::Attribute

to read the documentation with your favorite pager.
